  Text: |-
    The DepthModule allows developers to create a DepthFrameSession, which provides a continuous stream of DepthFrameData for real-time spatial understanding.
    
    After configuring your API tokens for the Remote Service Gateway, tap the microphone button and start asking questions about your surroundings.
    
    You’ll see spatial labels appear on nearby objects, demonstrating the powerful combination of AR and AI working seamlessly together.
